      "content": "that's a good start, very atmospheric. to make it feel even more real, i want to start introducing the people who live there. can you describe some of the types of people you'd see loitering on the corners or hanging out near those tenements? i want to capture that sense of \"unpredictability\" and the specific look of the locals that would make a stranger feel like they don't belong there.",
